r used.","'setTimeOver' is assigned a value but never used.","'initialTime' is assigned a value but never used.","'setInitialTime' is assigned a value but never used.","'setShow' is assigned a value but never used.","'teste' is assigned a value but never used.","'testStr' is assigned a value but never used.","jsx-a11y/img-redundant-alt","Redundant alt attribute. Screen-readers already announce `img` tags as an image. You don’t need to use the words `image`, `photo,` or `picture` (or any specified custom words) in the alt prop.","'Aux' is defined but never used.","'show' is assigned a value but never used.",["207"],["208"],"no-global-assign","no-unsafe-negation"]